commitResults.messageTitle: fix: Ignore case when comparing names in Name class
commitResults.messageBody:
Comparison of names is case-sensitive. This can cause issues
where names differing only in letter case were treated as distinct.

A case-insensitive comparison is more user-friendly because users
cannot be expected to remember the exact case of every name.

Let's,
* update the Name.java so that name comparisons are case-insensitive
